column2: SELECT   sp.objID,   s.dr7ObjID,   p.petroR5#_r,   p.petroR5#Err_r,   p.petroR9#_r,   p.petroR9#Err_r,   r.TYPE,   r.TYPEERR into mydb.MyTable  from SpecPhotoAll AS sp   JOIN SpecDR7 AS s ON sp.specObjID  = s.specObjID   JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p on sp.objID = p.objID   JOIN RC3 AS r ON r.objID = sp.objID WHERE   sp.petroMagErr_r < #   AND sp.petroMagErr_g < #   AND sp.petroMagErr_i < #   AND sp.z > #   AND sp.z < #   AND sp.petroMag_r < #   AND r.TYPE > #   ORDER BY sp.objID
